race.description: Bjb Plumbing & Gasfitting Country Boost Maiden Plt
race.comment: MAYBE NOW (4) was beaten a nose into second at this track two starts ago then finished fifth last time at Coonamble. Has a strong finish. Capable of sharp improvement and can get off the mark. NOTERBEL (10) hasn't been far away lately including a last-start third over 1200m at Forbes. Drawn to advantage and is sure to give backers another bold sight. PRIZUGA (6) struggles to break the ice but is knocking on the door after a narrow defeat last start over this trip at Orange after being in the firing line on the bend. Anticipating another big run. ROSIE I AM (12) closed off nicely when beaten 2 lengths last time at Bathurst.  Strips fitter third-up and can fight out the finish. THE BULLET (8) settled well back last time out then worked home well to finish fourth over 1100m at Narromine. Suited by the longer journey and is among the each-way chances.
